headline: Goldman Sachs Initiates Coverage of UnitedHealth Group Incorporated (UNH) with Buy Rating
summary: UnitedHealth Group Incorporated (NYSE:UNH) is among the 14 Best Big Name Stocks to Invest in Right Now. headline: Managed Care Insurers Trading Down Ahead Of Earnings Season
summary: US managed care insurers were trading down this week ahead of earnings season as the release of Medicare ratings and federal tax credit uncertainty appeared to weigh on stock prices.
